description: Primes p such that 95 is not a square mod p.
links: Vincenzo Librandi, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
prog: (MAGMA) [p: p in PrimesUpTo(457) | not IsSquare(R! 95) where R:= ResidueClassRing(p) ]; // _Vincenzo Librandi_, Sep 10 2012
